summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing execution of an agreement with the State of Washington, Department of Highways, for the allocation of federal funds in aid of the cost of preparation of plans, specifications and cost estimates, and of related preconstruction engineering work for the City's Stadium and CBD Traffic Control Project - Project No. 9999(4) under the Federal Highway Act of 1970, 23 U.S. Code, Highways, Federal Aid "M" Program.
